Package: work.tkgstrator.kioueditor
Name: KiouEditor
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: iphoneos-arm64
Description: Unlocks decoration supplies, characters, and skins in KIOU (Shogi) by editing the decoded SyncItemListReply in memory. Currency and paid items are never modified. For authorized testing only.
